snippet.title: Strip Poker 3 gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Strip Poker 3, Dos PC game produced by Artworx in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/strip-poker-3/1365/
Old but still enjoyable strip poker game, probably the most famous of Strip Poker dos games series.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
